===Noun===
'''fisticuffs''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#A [[derivative]] of [[boxing]] in which two [[opponent]]s tie either their right or left [[wrist]]s together and [[box]] with their free hands.
#(''informal'') An [[impromptu]] fight with the fists, usually between two people.

